data.description: Beautiful desirable single-family home in the heart of Naples, FL, BERKSHIRE VILLAGE AT BERKSHIRE LAKES.  Lakefront property with breathtaking views of the lake and nature. A 3 Bedroom 2 Bath, 2 car garage with volume ceilings throughout, screened-in porch, and lanai offering 29 feet of covered lanai space a perfect place to entertain family and friends or just enjoy the quiet and peaceful evenings of your home. The property has been recently painted, and a completely new Air Conditioning System with New Duct Work. New Water Heater, and Newer Roof. Centrally Located in the Heart of Naples, FL in the beautiful community of BERKSHIRE VILLAGE AT BERKSHIRE LAKES.  Transferable Flood Insurance Policy. This is a gem in the heart of Naples.
